Class SelectTileDialogController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controllers.SelectTileDialogController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InitialisableWithParameters

    public class SelectTileDialogController
extends java.lang.Object
implements InitialisableWithParameters
    Controller class for the Select Tile Dialog. Allows the player to chose and apply a TileEffect to a 3X3 grid of tiles.
    Version:
    1.2
    Author:
    Joseph Omar
